"wie wirke ich gerade?", "wie geht es mir laut meinen Daten?".
Speak the returned text as-is — it already names the data source.
Never diagnose; these are light behavioral observations only.",
        "name": "get_emotional_state",
        "parameters": {
          "properties": {},
          "required": [],
